{"tid":1910935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平機會：「岐視某人有病毒都算違例！」","createTime":"2020-03-05T04:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:13:08.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"95068f2edeca443405d2166bec32da4cb6cf3b0b","tid":1910935,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"「鑽石公主號」乘客張寶華為替黎芷珊補祝生日，在上海總會訂位被拒，有立法會議員建議她向平等機會委員會（EOC）投訴：<br />\n<br />\n「覺得也值得向平機會提出，我食個飯都會被歧視，其他人都一樣可能因為呢個病受到不公平的對待。所以向EOC投訴，目的不是要告上海總會，而是希望EOC可以提醒其他人別重蹈覆轍。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平機會指根據《殘疾歧視條例》，「殘疾」的定義包括體內可能引致疾病的有機體如病毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，殘疾的定義亦包括了曾經存在、未來可能存在或被認為存在的殘疾。因此，若服務提供者認定某些人士可能存有「殘疾」而拒絕提供服務，有可能違反《殘疾歧視條例》。"},{"pid":"95813447415f9d32b117c4bbaf56fda0921edd71","tid":1910935,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33583f8c9619f461ed49b3e561ccab97e68e3c7","tid":1910935,"uid":129664,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">殘疾的定義亦包括了曾經存在、未來可能存在或被認為存在的殘疾。</span><br />\n<br />\n即係全部人都係殘疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efb521880504c74a30145940571a91c7f0ecf0e","tid":1910935,"uid":197393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84fdac08fec284a4d46aa1c382352caad529e29","tid":1910935,"uid":240374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"岐視係你無辦法改變既事實而我對此有偏頗既反應<br />\n<br />\n芝麻人無一個係蘑菇的"},{"pid":"ff33aff1124a0c42cd60aef3cff6346cbd2548f9","tid":1910935,"uid":202464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score"